## 🛠️ 2. Samba Server Configuration (RHEL / CentOS / Rocky Linux)

### [Step 1] Install Packages & Prepare Directories
Install the core Samba packages and create the directory intended for network sharing.
```bash
# Install packages
sudo dnf install -y samba samba-common

# Create share directory
sudo mkdir -p /samba/share
sudo chmod 777 /samba/share  # For testing (restrict permissions using groups in production)
